🚀 1. ClusterIP
🔹 What is it?

Default service type — exposes service internally within the cluster.

🔹 Why?

For internal communication between services

🔹 Where used?

Backend → Database communication

🔹 How it works?

Assigns internal IP accessible only inside cluster

🎤 Interview Answer

“ClusterIP is used for internal communication between services within the cluster.”
